# OPS/_llm/90 — vector mode: embed the question.
#
# Runs only when KV/retrieval.jsonl is flipped to "vector" (see README
# for the one-time seeding of the "decisions" collection). Needs an
# embedding backend: "openai" (tenant secret OPENAI_KEY) or "ollama"
# for keyless local. Scope 92's search consumes @_embed.vector, so the
# producer→consumer pair sits in consecutive scopes, not one.
WHEN @src == "llm" && @llm.phase == "request" && ._retrieval.mode == "vector"
  WITH provider = "openai", model = "text-embedding-3-small", text = @_question
  EXEC "ai://embed"
